		<div class="block-contributor-content">
		<div class="block-contributor-bio small">
			<p><strong><span class="smallcaps">Sparrow</span></strong> lives with his wife, Violet, and daughter, Sylvia, in Phoenicia, New York. His new book is titled <em>America: A Prophecy</em> (Soft Skull Press). He was a <span class="smallcaps">TV</span> star for fifty-six seconds in 1996, and was interviewed in <em>TV Guide</em>.</p><a href="/contributors/sparrow" class="block-contributor-link link-alt small">More From This Contributor&nbsp;&#9656;</a>		</div>
